 Setting sun and lots of video billboards above Shibuya Crossing this evening.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
 今夜の夕焼けと、渋谷交差点の上にあるたくさんの映像看板。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Sunset" /><summary type="html">Setting sun and lots of video billboards above Shibuya Crossing this evening.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08527-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08527-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sekigahara・関ヶ原</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220531/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sekigahara・関ヶ原" /><published>2022-05-31T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-31T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sekigahara</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220531/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
 Farmland and mountains near &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sekigahara,_Gifu&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Sekigahara&lt;/a&gt; in Gifu Prefecture, location of one of the &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Battle_of_Sekigahara&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;most famous battles&lt;/a&gt; in Japanese history. View from the Shinkansen.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  岐阜県&lt;a href=&quot;https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%96%A2%E3%82%B1%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%BA&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;関ヶ原&lt;/a&gt;付近の農地と山。新幹線から撮影しました。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Japan" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html">Farmland and mountains near Sekigahara in Gifu Prefecture, location of one of the most famous battles in Japanese history. View from the Shinkansen.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_IMG_5654.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_IMG_5654.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Suspension Bridge・吊橋</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220529/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Suspension Bridge・吊橋" /><published>2022-05-29T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-29T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/suspension</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220529/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Spider builds a web suspended across the rocks.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  クモが岩に張り巡らされた巣を作る。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Hozu River" /><summary type="html">Spider builds a web suspended across the rocks.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08449-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08449-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hozu River・保津川</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220528/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hozu River・保津川" /><published>2022-05-28T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-28T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hozu</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220528/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Warm, lazy day, perfect for a peaceful ride on the Hozu River.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  暖かく晴れた日は、保津川を穏やかに走るのに最適な日です。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Hozu River" /><summary type="html">Warm, lazy day, perfect for a peaceful ride on the Hozu River.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_IMG_5621.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_IMG_5621.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Shio Koji・塩小路</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220527/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Shio Koji・塩小路" /><published>2022-05-27T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-27T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/shio-koji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220527/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
On one of the last days in Kyoto for a while, a sunny view of Kyoto Tower and the Kyoto Station area. Shio Koji is the name of the street at the bottom of the photo, and the name of this neighborhood.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  京都滞在終了間際、晴れた日の京都タワーと京都駅周辺の眺め。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Views" /><category term="Skylines" /><summary type="html">On one of the last days in Kyoto for a while, a sunny view of Kyoto Tower and the Kyoto Station area. Shio Koji is the name of the street at the bottom of the photo, and the name of this neighborhood.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08441.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08441.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Nintendo Hotel・ホテル任天堂</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220525/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Nintendo Hotel・ホテル任天堂" /><published>2022-05-25T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-25T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/nintendo</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220525/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  The &lt;a href=&quot;https://marufukuro.com/en&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Marufukuro Hotel&lt;/a&gt;, recently opened in the original 1889 headquarters of Nintendo. A beautiful example of &quot;Western style&quot; architecture from the Meiji Era.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nintendo.co.jp/corporate/en/index.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Nintendo‘s current headquarters&lt;/a&gt; are a few miles away.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  旧任天堂本社にオープンしたホテル「&lt;a href=&quot;https://marufukuro.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;丸福樓&lt;/a&gt;」。明治時代の洋風建築の美しい一例です。
  &lt;/p&gt;
  
  &lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;

  現在の&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nintendo.co.jp/corporate/index.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;任天堂本社&lt;/a&gt;はここから数キロのところにあります。
  &lt;/p&gt;
  
