&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  嵐山の竹林の前で、昼下がりの太陽に照らされるカエデの葉。天龍寺にて。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Foliage" /><category term="Tenryu-ji" /><category term="Bamboo Grove" /><summary type="html">Maple leaves lit by the late afternoon sun, in front of the Arashiyama bamboo grove. At Tenryu-ji Temple.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_IMG_5546.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_IMG_5546.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Togetsu Bridge・渡月橋</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220519/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Togetsu Bridge・渡月橋" /><published>2022-05-19T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-19T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/arashiyama</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220519/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
